race.comment: A few different form lines converge in this middle-distance contest. COLLATED (2) is progressive and won well last start. He's got a handy claim and can roll forward from the wide gate to race on or near the speed. He's got more upside than most and he will probably end up being the best horse in the race. He can win. TOWER OF TUSCANY (8) has been freshened up but looks ready to peak after a couple of minor placings. Play each-way. There has been a bit to like about the recent runs of the trio I LOVE THIS SONG (12), UTAH (9) and BIT OF A REBEL (1) who are all genuine top three candidates on best form.
